查询商户商品列表
接口：queryGoodsList.do
入参：{
		"merchantId":"",//商户ID
		"goodsName":"",//商品名称，模糊查询用
		"pageInfo":{
			"pageNum":"",//当前页
			"pageSize":""//每一页数据条数

		}
	  }

出参：{
		"errorCode":"",
		"errorMsg":"",
		"pageInfo":{
			"total":"",//总数据条数
			“pages":"",//总页数
			"pageNum":"",//当前页
			"pageSize":"",//每一页数据条数
			"list":[{
				"goodsId":"",//商品ID
				"merchantId":"",//商户ID
				"goodsName":"",//商品名称
				"goodsPrice":"",//商品单价
				"goodsAmount":""//商品数量
			}
			……
			]

		}
	  }


校验手环是否可消费,并拉出客户信息
接口：checkHandRing.do
入参：String handRingId//手环ID
	  String handRingCode//手环密码
出参：{
		"errorCode":"",
		"errorMsg":"",
		"customer":{
			"customerId":"",//客户ID
			“handRingId":"",//手环ID
			"phoneNumber":"",//手机号
			"idType":"",//证件类型
			"idNumber":"",//证件号
			"customerName":"",//客户姓名
			"accountBalance":""//账户余额

		}
	  }

